      <odd id="aspace_79d1ce174849a0cb161b305bc9b208cb">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 40 (YRG 40), Records of Yale clubs, societies, and organizations..</p>  
      </odd>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_95202dc78710aa9574c610902f351213">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The records were transferred from Mixed Company of Yale, 2008.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_b3da9c9c1de8f517b3ff84d01247e54d">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>The materials are open for research.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <userestrict id="aspace_b65e170ad110bd7e8a85f832a03ec018">
         <head>Conditions Governing Use</head>
         <p>Copyright for materials authored or otherwise produced as official business of Yale University is retained by Yale University. Copyright status for other collection materials is unknown. Transmission or reproduction of materials protected by U.S. Copyright Law (Title 17, U.S.C.) beyond that allowed by fair use requires the written permission of the copyright owners. Works not in the public domain cannot be commercially exploited without permission of the copyright owners. Responsibility for any use rests exclusively with the user.</p>  
      </userestrict>
      <prefercite id="aspace_cf05dd4daf4324a230ac147ab0bbb8ac">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Mixed Company of Yale Records (RU 1077). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <processinfo id="aspace_ce06db532458ec6bf0691520abc61dde">
         <head>Processing Information</head>
         <p>Yale University records are arranged and described at the accession level by the creating office. The University Archives creates collection level descriptive records, but typically does no further arrangement and description at the accession level.</p>  
      </processinfo>
      <separatedmaterial id="aspace_a971c2ecc524c6e85f09177236a67757">
         <head>Separated Materials</head>
         <p>Commercial audiorecordings were transferred to the Historical Sound Recordings Collection, Yale Music Library.</p>  
      </separatedmaterial>
      <bioghist id="aspace_09f764063f1e90c3a87c681a87300664">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>Mixed Company of Yale was founded in the fall of 1981.</p>  
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_dd31bab7d5f3d769c25c13f043a78deb">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of sheet music, advertisements, clippings, photographs, scrapbooks, and other memorabilia of Mixed Company at Yale.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement id="aspace_7c535d9d5d8232870f13386b1b8e4e1c">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged by type of material.</p>  
      </arrangement>
